  <refentryinfo><title>Jacko Opcodes</title></refentryinfo>
  <refmeta>
    <refentrytitle>JackoOn</refentrytitle>
  </refmeta>
  
  <refnamediv>
    <refname>JackoOn</refname>
    <refpurpose>
      Enables or disables all Jack ports.
    </refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <note>plugin: Requires jacko plugin</note>
  <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
      In the orchestra header, after all Jack connections have been created, enables
      or disables all Jack input and output opcodes 
      inside this instance of Csound to read or write data.
    </para>
  </refsect1>
  
  <refsect1>
    <title>Syntax</title>
    <synopsis><command>JackoOn </command>[iactive] </synopsis>
  </refsect1>
  
  <refsect1>
    <title>Initialization</title>
    <para>
      <emphasis>iactive</emphasis> -- A flag that turns the ports on 
      (the default) or off.
    </para>
  </refsect1>
  
